      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nIn the above autotest run, the filesystem size was equal to the device size which made the test case do nothing:\n\nCMD: client-6vm3 resize2fs  /dev/lvm-MDS/S1 \nclient-6vm3: resize2fs 1.42.7.wc1 (12-Apr-2013)\nclient-6vm3: The filesystem is already 26624 blocks long.  Nothing to do!\n\nI'm updating the test to shrink the filesystem first, then expand.",
